### PR-008

**Title**: Distributed rate-limit & quota observability with per-tenant dashboards
**Problem**: #4540 (auto combo ignores provider quota) and #4806 (quota exclusive listings) both stem from operators having no visibility into the per-tenant, per-provider quota state.
**Solution**:
- Emit metrics: `omniroute_quota_remaining{provider,model,tenant}`, `omniroute_quota_window_reset_at{provider,tenant}`, `omniroute_quota_denial_total{provider,tenant,reason}`.
