### PR-050

**Title**: Performance regression CI — automated k6 load tests on every PR
**Problem**: We have `tests/load/` but no CI integration. Regressions slip in.
**Solution**:
- New GitHub Actions workflow `.github/workflows/perf.yml` (200 LOC) running k6 scripts in `tests/load/k6/*.js` (8 new scripts, 1.2k LOC).
