- Files affected: `src/middleware/securityHeaders.ts` (new, 260 LOC), `src/middleware/cors/index.ts:1-200` (integrate), `src/server-init.ts:1-150` (mount), `src/app/layout.tsx:1-100` (extend metadata), `tests/unit/middleware/securityHeaders.test.ts` (new, 200 LOC), `tests/e2e/security/headers.spec.ts` (new, 130 LOC), `docs/security/06-headers.md` (new, 60 LOC).
