- Files affected: `src/lib/cliTools/tui/app.tsx` (new, 200 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/tui/state.ts` (new, 130 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/tui/keymap.ts` (new, 90 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/tui/panels/route.tsx` (new, 110 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/tui/panels/cache.tsx` (new, 100 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/tui/panels/quotas.tsx` (new, 100 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/tui/panels/logs.tsx` (new, 100 LOC), `bin/omniroute-tui.mjs` (new, 60 LOC), `package.json:200-260` (ink, ink-select-input), `tests/unit/cliTools/tui.test.ts` (new, 240 LOC), `docs/cli/08-tui.md` (new, 130 LOC).
**Test plan**: Render panels in jsdom; assert keymap drives transitions.
