### PR-070

**Title**: Profiling & tracing CLI (`omniroute profile`) using `node --inspect` and flame graphs
**Problem**: Performance regressions are hard to diagnose without a CPU profile.
**Solution**:
- New module `src/lib/cliTools/profile.ts` (320 LOC) wraps `node --inspect-brk`, captures a 30-second profile with `--prof`, and renders flame graphs via `pprof`.
- Files affected: `src/lib/cliTools/profile.ts` (new, 320 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/profile/parser.ts` (new, 130 LOC), `src/lib/cliTools/profile/flamegraph.ts` (new, 110 LOC), `bin/omniroute-profile.mjs` (new, 60 LOC), `package.json:200-260` (pprof, d3-flame-graph), `tests/unit/cliTools/profile.test.ts` (new, 240 LOC), `docs/cli/11-profile.md` (new, 90 LOC).
**Test plan**: Capture a profile under synthetic load; assert SVG rendered.
**Risk**: Low.
**Estimate**: L

